title: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
headline: This Month's GTA+ Benefits
subtitle: GTA+
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ Members who've signed up for this month (December 10 - January 8) will also receive:

— The new Bravado Banshee GTS (Sports)
— 40% off the new Master Control Terminal Terrorbyte Upgrade
— The Los Santos Tattoo Jeans and Los Santos Tattoo Tee
— Exclusive holiday apparel
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
